import { List, ListItemButton, ListItemIcon, ListItemText } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

function DrawerComp() {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
        <Drawer open={true}>
            <List>
                <ListItemButton>
                    <ListItemIcon>
                        <ListItemText>Login</ListItemText>
                    </ListItemIcon>
                </ListItemButton>
            </List>
        </Drawer>
        </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default DrawerComp
